query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.tenantId,
  t.name as tenant_name,
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  wl.code as location_code,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as available,
  i.status
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
WHERE p.sku = '401460P'
ORDER BY i.expiryDate;
